front.title: •Hol Okand
front.gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Gold 6 during battle, adds one destiny to total power only. When at Kashyyyk system, adds 1 to each of your Force drains there.
front.lore: Piloted Gold 6 at the Battle of Yavin. Flew as Dutch's wingman during an attack on an Imperial supply outpost at Kashyyyk. Befriended by Chewbacca before leaving Yavin 4.
